:47A:1. THREE PERCENT MORE OR LESS WITHIN EACH INDIVIDUAL QUANTITY AND
AMOUNT ARE ACCEPTABLE.
.
2. THIRD PARTY SHIPPER AND DOCUMENTS ARE ACCEPTABLE EXCEPT
COMMERCIAL INVOICE.
.
3. ALL CHARGES ARE FOR THE ACCOUNT OF BENEFICIARY EXCEPT L/C
ISSUING FEE.
.
4. INSURANCE TO BE COVERED BY ULTIMATE BUYER.
.
5. UPON INSTRUCTION OF TOM TAILOR SOURCING LIMITED WE AGREE TO A
PREMATURE DISCOUNTED PAYMENT OF THE AMOUNT OF THE CREDIT
ACCORDING TO THE VALUE OF THE DOCUMENTS PRESENTED.THE DISCOUNTING
WILL BE EFFECTED AT THE RATE OF COST OF FUNDS + 1.5PCT P.A. MIN
USD100 AS ON THE DISCOUNTING DATE. THE AMOUNT OF THE DISCOUNT IS
CALCULATED FROM THE DAY ON WHICH WE ARRANGE FOR THE DISCOUNTED
PROCEEDS OF THE DOCUMENTS. THE REQUEST FOR PREMATURE DISCOUNTING
CAN BE MADE BY WRITING: FOR IMMEDIATE DISCOUNTING AS PER THE L/C
TERMS ON THE COMMERCIAL INVOICE OR ON THE DOCUMENTARY REMITTANCE
LETTER OF THE PRESENTING BANK. ALL DISCOUNT CHARGES ARE FOR
BENEFICIARIES ACCOUNT.
.
6.A DISCREPANCY FEE OF USD90.00 (OR EQUIVALENT) WILL BE LEVIED
WHEN IT IS NECESSARY TO CONTACT THE APPLICANT IN RESPECT OF ANY
DISCREPANT DOCUMENTS PRESENTED UNDER THE L/C.THE DISCREPANCY FEE
WILL BE DEDUCTED FROM PROCEEDS INCLUDING ANY TELEX CHARGES
INVOLVED.
.
7. UNLESS OTHERWISE STIPULATED IN THE CREDIT, ALL DOCUMENTS MUST
BE PRESENTED IN ORIGINAL.
.
8. NOTWITHSTANDING THE PROVISIONS OF UCP600, IF WE GIVE NOTICE OF
REFUSAL OF DOCUMENTS PRESENTED UNDER THIS CREDIT WE SHALL HOWEVER
RETAIN THE RIGHT TO ACCEPT A WAIVER OF DISCREPANCIES FROM THE
APPLICANT AND, SUBJECT TO SUCH WAIVER BEING ACCEPTABLE TO US, TO
RELEASE DOCUMENTS AGAINST THAT WAIVER WITHOUT REFERENCE TO THE
PRESENTER PROVIDED THAT NO WRITTEN INSTRUCTIONS TO THE CONTRARY
HAVE BEEN RECEIVED BY US FROM THE PRESENTER BEFORE THE RELEASE OF
THE DOCUMENTS. ANY SUCH RELEASE PRIOR TO RECEIPT OF CONTRARY
INSTRUCTIONS SHALL NOT CONSTITUTE A FAILURE ON OUR PART TO HOLD
THE DOCUMENTS AT THE PRESENTER'S RISK AND DISPOSAL, AND WE WILL
HAVE NO LIABILITY TO THE PRESENTER IN RESPECT OF ANY SUCH
RELEASE.
.
9. ALL DOCUMENTS SUBMITTED UNDER THIS LC MUST BE ISSUED IN
ENGLISH LANGUAGE UNLESS OTHERWISE SPECIFIED IN THE CREDIT
.
10. DOCUMENTS TO BE PRESENTED WITHIN 11 DAYS AFTER THE DATE OF
SHIPMENT BUT WITHIN THE VALIDITY OF CREDIT.
.
11. PLEASE READ BENEFICIARY NAME AND ADDRESS AS BELOW,
